Question: Fly Cat Electrical Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Fly Cat Electrical Co., Ltd.

Oral Irrigator

- Professional manufacturer of oral and nasal irrigators
- Offers customization options, low MOQ, and steady supply
- Products range from oral irrigators to nasal irrigation devices
- 10 years of experience in R&D and OEM/ODM
- Offers extensive customization options from material to packaging
- Products guided by ISO and SGS quality management
- Offers efficient and strong water pressure, three modes, and a large detachable reservoir
- Cordless, compact, and travel-size design
- Comes with 4 tips, 2 tip cases, and a USB charger
- 3 modes: normal, slow, and pulse, suitable for various dental needs
